      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/540578889_2015236489305204_7318634461119339149_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_p360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=104&amp;ig_cache_key=MzcwOTY4Mjg2MTA1NDkyNjg3NQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjY0MHg4MDAuc2RyLkMzIn0%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=mUuCOqeBBosQ7kNvwHyk3nn&amp;_nc_oc=AdrwBLQ9XxKeGc3Q3TxVLp9O4weOVLlO9EJMw8OFhdOkU4OZ3fpDigBqO4y4UETcSeE&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=hhol79PniGioZqGS1FjI7Q&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfxlknupWX1YjGC85Apq1QIUwaK0WbxSiiWJ2qgh_tn49w&amp;oe=69C9B189" alt="Instagram billede fra @peter_folkmar" /></p><p><strong>@peter_folkmar</strong></p><p>SO DAMN PROUD! 🥳 In two weeks the next iteration of @postfestival takes place in Copenhagen. Curated, designed and communicated by an amazing group of people: @albaaaccc @bethany.rigby @filipgronning @georginalnorris @lucasfeldstedt @kaiums_ ♻️ This time we are discussing the life cycle of visual design with a stellar line-up of creatives &amp; critics 🔝 As the festival in running entirely on voluntary energy, we are grateful for the essential support of @hkgrafiskkommunikation @trifolium_cph and @arkitekterogdesignere -- and lastly all ticket holders! Thanks for your support ❤️‍🔥</p>]]></description>
